00:14:15.343 --> 00:14:16.345
- Take them.

00:14:16.378 --> 00:14:18.348
- Huh? Really, for me?

00:14:21.455 --> 00:14:23.693
What? Thank you!

00:14:23.727 --> 00:14:25.897
I promise you
I'll treasure them!

00:14:26.733 --> 00:14:28.771
- There's no need
to treasure them.

00:14:28.804 --> 00:14:29.773
- Huh?

00:14:29.806 --> 00:14:31.943
Ah, no way.

00:14:31.976 --> 00:14:34.114
That would be such a waste.

00:14:35.216 --> 00:14:36.218
- It's fine.

00:14:39.091 --> 00:14:42.765
If they get ripped,
then I'll give you a new pair.

00:14:42.799 --> 00:14:44.669
- [laughs]

00:14:44.703 --> 00:14:45.904
Mm!

00:14:49.010 --> 00:14:51.716
<i>I've often found myself
thinking things like,</i>

00:14:51.749 --> 00:14:53.820
<i>"Should a girl be this strong?"</i>

00:14:53.853 --> 00:14:55.791
<i>Would people
start saying yet again</i>

00:14:55.825 --> 00:14:58.128
<i>that I couldn't be human
if I were?</i>

00:14:58.162 --> 00:15:01.903
<i>I've been so afraid, that I've
been holding back my power.</i>

00:15:02.738 --> 00:15:04.107
<i>But I'm through with that.</i>

00:15:04.141 --> 00:15:07.313
- Ms. Kanroji's
our only ray of hope!

00:15:07.347 --> 00:15:08.249
- [grunts]

00:15:08.282 --> 00:15:10.386
- Huh? [growls]
- [drum pounds]

00:15:12.256 --> 00:15:14.060
- [roars]

00:15:14.962 --> 00:15:16.231
[Kanroji] Just leave it to me.

00:15:16.265 --> 00:15:18.804
I'll protect you all,
no matter what!

00:15:18.837 --> 00:15:21.642
<i>[heroic music]</i>

00:15:26.017 --> 00:15:27.220
[drums pound]

00:15:29.357 --> 00:15:32.063
I'll take care of this one
by myself!

00:15:36.640 --> 00:15:39.745
You guys go on ahead!
Defeat the main body!

00:15:39.778 --> 00:15:41.616
- Nezuko! Genya!

00:15:41.649 --> 00:15:43.051
- [grunts]
- [grunts]

00:15:45.322 --> 00:15:46.158
- [roars]

00:15:46.191 --> 00:15:49.264
<i>- I've got to increase
my heart rate.</i>

00:15:49.298 --> 00:15:51.669
<i>I need to speed up
my circulation.</i>

00:15:51.702 --> 00:15:53.540
<i>Move faster.</i>

00:15:53.573 --> 00:15:54.943
<i>Hit stronger!</i>

00:15:54.976 --> 00:15:56.646
<i>More!</i>

00:15:56.679 --> 00:15:58.616
[drums pound]

00:16:00.954 --> 00:16:02.991
<i>- You little brats.</i>

00:16:03.794 --> 00:16:04.762
- [growls]

00:16:04.795 --> 00:16:05.998
- [gasps]

00:16:06.031 --> 00:16:13.212
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:16:15.016 --> 00:16:16.318
<i>[singer vocalizing]</i>

00:16:16.351 --> 00:16:18.456
- If you want to get
to my comrades,

00:16:18.489 --> 00:16:21.228
then you're gonna
have to get through me!

00:16:22.698 --> 00:16:25.770
- Tanjiro! Where's the thing
with the main body?

00:16:25.804 --> 00:16:26.773
Can you track it?

00:16:26.806 --> 00:16:27.775
- I'll try!

00:16:27.808 --> 00:16:35.022
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:16:38.529 --> 00:16:39.732
- [whimpering]

00:16:39.765 --> 00:16:41.034
- Found it!

00:16:41.903 --> 00:16:43.305
This way!

00:16:43.339 --> 00:16:47.179
<i>Ms. Kanroji can only hold off
that child demon for so long.</i>

00:16:47.213 --> 00:16:50.419
<i>We have to slash the main
body before it's too late!</i>

00:16:52.290 --> 00:16:53.793
- Hmph.

00:16:53.827 --> 00:16:55.096
<i>- This young girl,</i>

00:16:55.129 --> 00:16:57.935
<i>she's moving
even faster than before!</i>

00:16:57.968 --> 00:16:59.037
<i>I don't understand.</i>

00:16:59.071 --> 00:17:00.574
<i>What's happening?</i>

00:17:00.607 --> 00:17:02.143
<i>How is she...</i>

00:17:03.914 --> 00:17:05.183
<i>A mark?</i>

00:17:05.216 --> 00:17:06.953
<i>Did she always have that?</i>

00:17:06.987 --> 00:17:08.657
<i>That...</i>

00:17:08.690 --> 00:17:11.328
<i>looks like a demon's crest.</i>

00:17:12.764 --> 00:17:14.067
[drums pound]

00:17:16.205 --> 00:17:18.776
<i>This is beyond annoying!</i>

00:17:18.810 --> 00:17:20.614
<i>Thanks to
this slip of a girl,</i>

00:17:20.647 --> 00:17:23.318
<i>I can't unleash my dragons
on those brats!</i>

00:17:27.527 --> 00:17:28.997
<i>Despicable!</i>

00:17:29.030 --> 00:17:32.070
<i>Nevertheless,
it won't last forever.</i>

00:17:32.103 --> 00:17:34.976
<i>She'll run out
of stamina eventually,</i>

00:17:35.009 --> 00:17:37.547
<i>the way all humans do!</i>

00:17:39.752 --> 00:17:43.893
- I will protect them,
no matter the cost!

00:17:43.927 --> 00:17:45.429
[running footsteps]

00:17:45.462 --> 00:17:47.969
- [gasps] There!

00:17:48.002 --> 00:17:50.039
It's inside that tree!

00:17:50.072 --> 00:17:51.175
- [whimpering]

00:17:51.208 --> 00:17:52.410
<i>- I'm positive.</i>

00:17:53.547 --> 00:17:56.352
<i>The demon
is hiding inside of it!</i>

00:17:56.385 --> 00:17:57.453
Hurry!

00:17:57.487 --> 00:17:58.455
[Nezuko grunts]

00:17:58.488 --> 00:18:01.494
- [yells]

00:18:01.529 --> 00:18:02.731
- Almost there!

00:18:02.765 --> 00:18:05.369
- Get outta there, you bastard!

00:18:09.979 --> 00:18:10.947
- [winces]

00:18:10.981 --> 00:18:12.918
[Nezuko grunting]

00:18:12.951 --> 00:18:15.924
- Don't let it shake you off!
Hang on!

00:18:15.957 --> 00:18:18.730
Hang on!
We have to strike it down

00:18:18.763 --> 00:18:22.671
before that snake-dragon thing
starts heading this way!

00:18:22.704 --> 00:18:25.610
While Ms. Kanroji's stopping it
from attacking!

00:18:25.644 --> 00:18:27.213
- [grunts]

00:18:27.246 --> 00:18:30.219
<i>- I can't swing my sword
while holding on!</i>

00:18:30.253 --> 00:18:33.258
<i>But I can still do this!</i>

00:18:34.060 --> 00:18:35.296
[growls]

00:18:35.330 --> 00:18:37.100
<i>- Whoa! He's biting it!</i>

00:18:37.133 --> 00:18:39.137
<i>His teeth are crazy strong!</i>

00:18:39.171 --> 00:18:41.108
But won't that upset
your stomach?

00:18:41.141 --> 00:18:43.513
Genya! Are you gonna be okay?!

00:18:46.118 --> 00:18:48.957
<i>- If I devour demons,
it's only temporary,</i>

00:18:48.990 --> 00:18:51.327
<i>but I can gain demonic traits!</i>

00:18:52.831 --> 00:18:55.103
<i>If I consume a strong demon,</i>

00:18:55.136 --> 00:18:57.173
<i>it boosts
my regenerative abilities</i>

00:18:57.206 --> 00:18:59.077
<i>and increases
my muscular strength!</i>

00:18:59.111 --> 00:19:01.314
[grunting]

00:19:03.720 --> 00:19:08.663
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:19:08.696 --> 00:19:09.765
<i>- It's down!</i>

00:19:10.767 --> 00:19:11.569
<i>Now!</i>

00:19:11.602 --> 00:19:13.540
- [tendrils whipping]
- [winces]

00:19:13.573 --> 00:19:15.944
<i>The branches are like whips.</i>

00:19:15.978 --> 00:19:17.648
<i>Stand your ground!</i>

00:19:17.681 --> 00:19:18.916
<i>Keep moving!</i>

00:19:21.723 --> 00:19:23.225
- [grunts]

00:19:27.299 --> 00:19:29.705
<i>- Nezuko's Blood Demon Art.</i>

00:19:29.739 --> 00:19:30.740
- [grunts]

00:19:30.774 --> 00:19:33.914
<i>- Thanks to the flames,
it's sluggish now!</i>

00:19:33.947 --> 00:19:34.949
<i>This will work.</i>

00:19:34.982 --> 00:19:35.951
<i>I can do this!</i>

00:19:35.984 --> 00:19:38.957
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:19:38.990 --> 00:19:41.128
Hinokami Kagura...

00:19:41.161 --> 00:19:42.363
Flame Dance!

00:19:43.465 --> 00:19:45.937
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:19:45.970 --> 00:19:47.774
<i>I still haven't landed a hit.</i>

00:19:50.581 --> 00:19:53.653
<i>This won't end
until I behead the main body!</i>

00:19:53.687 --> 00:19:56.058
- Tanjiro, do it!

00:19:56.091 --> 00:19:59.363
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:20:00.967 --> 00:20:02.136
<i>- It's gone!</i>

00:20:02.170 --> 00:20:05.811
<i>It must have run off again.
But where?!</i>

00:20:05.844 --> 00:20:07.814
<i>It can't have gotten that far.</i>

00:20:09.050 --> 00:20:10.520
[leaves rustle]

00:20:11.321 --> 00:20:12.490
[leaves rustle]

00:20:12.524 --> 00:20:13.993
- [yelps]

00:20:14.995 --> 00:20:17.567
- [gasps] Bastard!

00:20:17.601 --> 00:20:20.038
- [whimpering]
- Get back here!

00:20:20.072 --> 00:20:22.744
You can't run away
from your sins!

00:20:22.778 --> 00:20:26.552
Every atrocity you've committed,
every evil deed,

00:20:26.585 --> 00:20:30.259
I'm going to make you pay
for everything you've ever done!

00:20:30.292 --> 00:20:32.564
You're not escaping me!

00:20:36.673 --> 00:20:38.442
[man] No one else
can take responsibility

00:20:38.475 --> 00:20:40.212
for what you've done.

00:20:40.246 --> 00:20:42.651
It has to be you and you alone!

00:20:42.685 --> 00:20:46.057
You no-good,
two-faced, shameless liar!

00:20:46.091 --> 00:20:50.967
<i>- Ever since the day I was
born into this accursed world,</i>

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:53.438
<i>I've never once uttered a lie.</i>

00:20:53.472 --> 00:20:55.777
<i>I'm a virtuous weakling.</i>

00:20:55.810 --> 00:21:01.488
<i>As pitiful as I am,
nobody shows me any sympathy!</i>

00:21:01.523 --> 00:21:02.692
I...

00:21:02.725 --> 00:21:04.628
[crying]

00:21:04.662 --> 00:21:05.830
I...

00:21:06.833 --> 00:21:08.970
I've never told a lie!

00:21:09.003 --> 00:21:12.010
[crying]

00:21:12.043 --> 00:21:13.813
- Come on. Nezuko! Genya!

00:21:13.847 --> 00:21:14.815
- [grunts]

00:21:14.849 --> 00:21:15.850
- [growls]

00:21:16.919 --> 00:21:18.221
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:21:18.255 --> 00:21:20.660
[grunting]

00:21:21.662 --> 00:21:24.635
You bastard!

00:21:26.404 --> 00:21:31.749
I'm putting an end to this,
you stubborn moron!

00:21:33.619 --> 00:21:34.888
- [wails]

00:21:37.995 --> 00:21:41.201
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:21:41.234 --> 00:21:42.872
- [yells]

00:21:42.905 --> 00:21:44.876
<i>["Koi Kogare" playing]</i>

00:21:44.909 --> 00:21:51.922
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:23:12.984 --> 00:23:14.522
[page rustles]

00:23:14.555 --> 00:23:17.861
- Ms. Kanroji, thank you
for protecting all of us.

00:23:17.895 --> 00:23:20.967
You have my word.
We'll defeat that demon!

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:22.571
- [grunts]
- [grunts]

00:23:22.605 --> 00:23:25.510
- Now it's time
for a Taisho-era secret!

00:23:25.544 --> 00:23:26.879
Get a load of this.

00:23:26.912 --> 00:23:30.820
Eating 170 sakura rice cakes
every day for eight months

00:23:30.854 --> 00:23:34.026
caused Ms. Kanroji's hair
and eyes to change their color.

00:23:34.060 --> 00:23:36.431
- Wow. Is that true?

00:23:36.464 --> 00:23:38.603
- This is Ms. Kanroji
we're talking about.

00:23:38.636 --> 00:23:41.675
I don't know. I feel
like it's impossible to eat

00:23:41.709 --> 00:23:44.180
that many sakura rice cakes
without needi--

00:23:44.214 --> 00:23:45.784
- Here! For you, Muichiro!

00:23:45.817 --> 00:23:47.119
- Ms. Kanroji!

00:23:47.153 --> 00:23:49.692
- Why don't you take one
for yourself, Tanjiro?

00:23:49.725 --> 00:23:51.027
- Thank you very much!

00:23:52.029 --> 00:23:53.299
These are really good!

00:23:53.332 --> 00:23:55.135
Next, the final episode,

00:23:55.169 --> 00:23:58.609
"A Connected Bond:
Daybreak and First Light."

00:23:58.643 --> 00:23:59.778
No way are we going to let

00:23:59.812 --> 00:24:01.882
some arrogant demon
have his way!

00:24:01.916 --> 00:24:03.152
- That's right.

00:24:03.185 --> 00:24:04.320
- Let's give our all!

00:24:04.354 --> 00:24:05.455
- No way we're gonna lose!

00:24:05.489 --> 00:24:06.692
- [grunts]

